Running tests
=============

Run:

  yarn test

Just one single select test:

  yarn test --watch -t 'deep nested selectors'



Docker
======

Build:

   docker build -t minimalcss:tests .

Run:

   docker container run -it -t minimalcss:tests

Bash:

   docker container run -it -t minimalcss:tests bash


How to debug an csstree AST object in
=====================================

JSON.stringify(csstree.parse(text), null, 4)


Publishing on npmjs
===================

https://docs.npmjs.com/getting-started/publishing-npm-packages


1) Edit CHANGELOG.md

2)

npm version patch
...or...
npm version minor
...or...
npm version major

3)

git push --tags origin master
npm publish
